close_reason: "Continuation audit completed with release, npm, GitHub, temp install, changelog, package doctor, pm validation, commit, and push evidence recorded."
body: "This item records the current continuation audit separately from the original 0.1.0 release epic so the new verification evidence is traceable. Scope includes package metadata, GitHub repository state, npm registry visibility, pm package installability, release scripts, self-generated changelog, strict pm validation, and repository cleanliness."
